Printed on American Apparel 4.3 oz 100% cotton garment with soft inks for that "oh so nice" feel .

Try Hard,Never Settle,Stay Hungry...that's the motto around here. You are either with us, you're in our way... let's go either way!

description:
Here's the story.The original Footsies colorway was rocking, but I decided to do one my way for the fans.This is the FAVORITE COLOR COMBINATION of the Footsies shirt rocked out for the fans to wear one more time with a new feel and different eyes to it. So if you slept, this is your shot,if your old one is worn out...this is also your shot.Don't sleep.

Printed on 4.3 oz American Apparel tee 100% cotton using super soft waterbased inks for a light feel to the tee.In other words: this is a premium garment.

description: It's you against the world in this one..They may call you a scrub now, but not even 50 Ninjaz can hold you down if you keep your head up.

description: Clean shirt with a funky message: STAY AWAY FROM STINKERS. This tee comes clean about how we feel:If something smells fishy, it probably is.Deodorant is recommended in addition to this garment.

Printed on American Apparel 4.3 oz 100% cotton garment with soft inks for that "oh so nice" feel .

***PREORDER: This is a quickie preorder set to ship out mid-July.It helps to get your size early and once we reach a certain point, we will no longer take preorders either.This is really a limited run for the fans.So take advantage,and as always,if we get a shipment early and it's a preorder,it goes out that same day***

name: Mystery Tee
description:
The official tee of Gambler's Paradise.You pick a size, we pick a tee.It could be anything we have in stock.Samples,discontinued pieces,you name it.

If you like to party, this is your way to rock out on the cheap.Limited quantities,so go crazy while you can! 

NOTE: No returns or special requests are taken on this one, you get what you get,that's part of the gamble.
